clipkeeper (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Encrypt clipboard history with Fernet (AES-128-CBC + HMAC).
  * Machine-derived key via PBKDF2 + /etc/machine-id.
  * File permissions restricted to 0600.
  * Auto-migrate old plaintext history.json.
  * Falls back to XOR obfuscation without cryptography package.

 -- Daniel Nylander <daniel@danielnylander.se>  Tue, 04 Mar 2026 14:15:00 +0100

